query:
INSERT INTO ingredientConversions (restaurantId, ingredientId, fromUnit, toUnit, conversionFactor, notes)
SELECT 
    restaurantId,
    id,
    'pc',
    'lb',
    0.09375,
    'U10 Hokkaido scallops: 1 piece = 1.5 oz = 0.09375 lb'
FROM ingredients
WHERE name LIKE '%Scallops%'
ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE 
    conversionFactor = 0.09375, 
    notes = 'U10 Hokkaido scallops: 1 piece = 1.5 oz = 0.09375 lb';
